tios between Th and rare-earth\nelements, such as Eu, in very metal-poor stars. In order to apply the Th/Eu\nratios to estimates of stellar ages, further understanding for the Th\nproduction by the r-process nucleosynthesis is required.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Feb 2004 16:41:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
