nction of the applied magnetic flux.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Feb 2004 11:10:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2005 15:48:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
